        <name>XV_vcresampler_ConfigTable</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Configuration table for <ref refid="struct_x_v__vcresampler" kindref="compound">XV_vcresampler</ref> instances. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This table contains the configuration parameters for each instance of the <ref refid="struct_x_v__vcresampler" kindref="compound">XV_vcresampler</ref> hardware IP core. Each entry specifies the hardware properties and capabilities of a particular instance.</para><para>Fields:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>compatible: String identifying the compatible hardware version.</para></listitem><listitem><para>reg: Base address of the hardware instance.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,samples-per-clock: Number of samples processed per clock cycle.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,num-video-components: Number of video components supported.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,max-cols: Maximum number of columns (horizontal resolution).</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,max-rows: Maximum number of rows (vertical resolution).</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,max-data-width: Maximum data width supported.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,convert-type: Type of color conversion supported.</para></listitem><listitem><para>xlnx,num-v-taps: Number of vertical filter taps.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para>The table is terminated by an entry with a NULL compatible field. </para>        </detaileddescription>
