        <briefdescription>
<para>Looks up the configuration structure for the VCR resampler based on the provided base address. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function searches the XV_vcresampler_ConfigTable for an entry whose BaseAddress matches the specified BaseAddress. If BaseAddress is zero, the first entry is returned. If a matching configuration is found, a pointer to the configuration structure is returned; otherwise, NULL is returned.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>BaseAddress</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The base address of the VCR resampler instance to look up.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>Pointer to the matching <ref refid="struct_x_v__vcresampler___config" kindref="compound">XV_vcresampler_Config</ref> structure if found, otherwise NULL. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
